.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, jazz, funk, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, lacrosse, cricket, soccer
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
4. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of funk is between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | funk           | gospel | indie  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse   | cricket |

