.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, ambient, classical, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, van, trike, boat
1. the fan of ambient is the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the fan of trance is between the person driving the train and the fan of classical##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | ambient | trance | classical      |
| Transport     | trike | train    | van  | boat |

