.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, golf, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, subway, boat, train
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is golf and the person driving the boat##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | snowboarding | handball | golf     | surfing   |
| Transport   | boat   | subway     | train | trike |

