.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, mechanic, bartender, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, trike, subway, motorbike
1. the bartender is between the person driving the taxi and the engineer##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | mechanic | bartender | engineer | electrician |
| Transport   | taxi         | motorbike       | trike    | subway         |

