.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, artichoke, grapefruit, cabbage
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, basketball, snowboarding, cycling
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person eating artichoke and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | cabbage   | grapefruit      | artichoke   | banana  |
| Sport   | cycling | basketball | snowboarding | climbing |

