.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, cabbage, plum, avocado
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, adventure, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating avocado and the person eating pomegranate##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | pomegranate     | cabbage | avocado   | plum        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure   | disaster | zombie |

