.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, dancing, chess, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, funk, hip-hop
1. the fan of funk is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the fan of r&b is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing | chess | sudoku | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | funk          | r&b     | hip-hop  | classical     |

