2. the lawyer is between the person watching superhero movies and the teacher##2
3. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | teacher | lawyer | videographer | dancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | mystery    | superhero   | spy |

