.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, mexican, indian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, train, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the indonesian is the person driving the train##1
3. the indian is between the person driving the train and the mexican##2
4. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | indian | indonesian |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | quad-bike   | skateboard | train  |

