.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, malaysian, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, fish, guinea-pig
1. the argentine is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the nigerian is the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the horse and the british##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | british | argentine | malaysian |
| Pet           | fish  | guinea-pig  | mouse | horse      |

