The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, skiing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the indian is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the russian and the malaysian##2
5. the malaysian is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indian   | russian   | nigerian | malaysian |
| Sport         | rugby | water-polo | skateboarding     | skiing    |

