.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, collecting, cooking, fishing
4 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, frog, turtle
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | cooking    | fishing     | gardening | collecting |
| Pet     | lizard | turtle | frog       | rat     |

 